*** BUILDER OFFERING $15,000 INCENTIVE + 0.5% OF LOAN AMOUNT FROM BUILDER'S PREFERRED LENDER. ***  Don't miss your chance to make this CUSTOM NEW BUILD from SANDOR HOMES yours today. Located in Mystic River and just a few steps from the Leon River, this stunning four-bedroom, 3.5-bath home has STORAGE EVERYWHERE. You may never need to use the attic! Other features include granite countertops, vaulted ceilings, an open floor plan, a cozy wood-burning FIREPLACE, and an office. The luxurious kitchen has CUSTOM SOFT-CLOSE CABINETRY, a kitchen island, under-cabinet lighting, and energy-efficient stainless steel appliances. Behind the BARN DOOR is a vast walk-in pantry spacious enough to store lots of small appliances. 
Retire to the privacy of a split floor plan at the end of a long day. At the end of the day, retire to the privacy of the primary suite, which includes dual vanities, a garden tub, and a walk-in shower. The secondary bedroom has a private full bathroom, making it the perfect space for guests, teens, or grandparents. Pack your bags, and let's get you moved in today.
